 We provide two different distributions of SPIDER, one for 
UNIX workstations and a second VAX/VMS distribution for DEC
Alpha workstations.  At this time, we strongly recommend running 
SPIDER/WEB on a SGI workstation.  We will 
<A HREF="endvms.html"> phase out</A> the release of SPIDER for 
VAX/VMS during 1997.  <P>
